285
00:21:36,153 --> 00:21:40,883
The law of the jungle is the survival of the fittest.

286
00:21:40,883 --> 00:21:45,103
It's called the truth of natural selection, my boy.

287
00:21:46,633 --> 00:21:50,913
Why don't you give this work to Shim Hyung Woo, your attack dog?

288
00:21:50,913 --> 00:21:54,223
He'll hunt it down for you at your command.

289
00:22:21,233 --> 00:22:24,243
You can't afford leisure time right now.

290
00:22:24,243 --> 00:22:27,813
The big problem is not having a cigarette, but time. Do you have one?

291
00:22:27,813 --> 00:22:30,643
I thought you said you worked hard to quit for your son.

292
00:22:31,893 --> 00:22:34,313
- What's wrong? 
 - A light.

293
00:22:36,053 --> 00:22:38,053
Oh, Man. I forgot my lighter!

294
00:22:38,053 --> 00:22:40,123
I'm not in the mood for jokes right now!

295
00:22:40,123 --> 00:22:43,123
What about me? Do I look like I want to joke?

296
00:22:43,123 --> 00:22:45,613
Hey, you're the son of a successful V.P. What's the problem?

297
00:22:45,613 --> 00:22:49,323
Forget your being older; I feel I could punch you right now.

298
00:22:50,403 --> 00:22:52,963
It must be due to the V.P.

299
00:22:52,963 --> 00:22:55,463
I need to quit this job or something.

300
00:22:55,463 --> 00:22:57,703
Quitting accounting sounds good too!

301
00:22:57,703 --> 00:22:59,763
At least you won't hear any more bullsh*t.

302
00:22:59,763 --> 00:23:02,863
Why? Did Shim Hyung Woo say something?

303
00:23:05,533 --> 00:23:09,513
He's telling me to accept a new recruit for People's Entertainment's audit team.

304
00:23:09,513 --> 00:23:12,593
When the auditing process is nearly finished? Who?

305
00:23:12,593 --> 00:23:14,583
Jang Ho Woo,

306
00:23:14,583 --> 00:23:16,413
the high school graduate you selected.

307
00:23:16,413 --> 00:23:19,623
"Jang Ho Woo"? Did he say he would?

308
00:23:19,623 --> 00:23:21,233
The new recruit doesn't have a choice.

309
00:23:21,233 --> 00:23:24,103
He can only do what they tell him to do.

310
00:23:27,153 --> 00:23:29,423
   

311
00:23:32,743 --> 00:23:35,553
 Jang Ho Woo, come to my office. 

312
00:24:09,633 --> 00:24:13,953
Do you know your responsibilities on the People's Entertainment audit team?

313
00:24:13,953 --> 00:24:18,583
I heard from Manager Woo Sang Hyun that doing nothing is my job.

314
00:24:18,583 --> 00:24:24,663
I understand I should just stay quiet, then report the meeting minutes to Director Shim Hyung Woo.

315
00:24:24,663 --> 00:24:27,653
Woo Sang Hyun recommended you.

316
00:24:27,653 --> 00:24:29,193
How do you know each other?

317
00:24:29,193 --> 00:24:32,423
I've helped him with a few small tasks in the past.

318
00:24:32,423 --> 00:24:34,653
He wouldn't recommend you due to that.

319
00:24:34,653 --> 00:24:37,413
If things go wrong, he's responsible.

320
00:24:37,413 --> 00:24:41,653
With the confirmation letter, I guess you work hard doing others' work.

321
00:24:41,653 --> 00:24:44,873
So that one day it might become my work.

322
00:24:44,873 --> 00:24:48,943
My goal is to become a valuable talent at Taeil Accounting,

323
00:24:49,823 --> 00:24:52,193
like you, Director Shim Hyung Woo.

324
00:24:54,413 --> 00:24:56,653
 That guy, Jang Ho Woo... 

325
00:24:56,653 --> 00:25:00,663
I'll find out what happened with him; just do what Shim Hyung Woo wants for now.

326
00:25:00,663 --> 00:25:02,773
That's a safer route.

327
00:25:02,773 --> 00:25:05,393
Also, learn to hold your tongue.

328
00:25:05,393 --> 00:25:10,993
If it was easy, do you think Shim Hyung Woo, whom I trained, would be my superior now?

329
00:25:14,803 --> 00:25:16,703
Why? Are you leaving?

330
00:25:16,703 --> 00:25:19,923
If we're sending the audit report, we should do it on time.

331
00:25:19,923 --> 00:25:22,143
What a devoted accountant you are.

332
00:25:22,143 --> 00:25:26,403
Thank you. I feel a lot better after just taking a sniff of it.

333
00:25:26,403 --> 00:25:29,333
I could keep my promise to my son about quitting.

334
00:25:30,613 --> 00:25:32,403
Bye now.

335
00:25:50,433 --> 00:25:51,313
   

336
00:25:54,543 --> 00:25:59,063
In my next life, I wish I could be studious like you!

337
00:25:59,063 --> 00:26:00,943
