338
00:26:00,943 --> 00:26:04,503
To personally develop ideas or patents I devise.

339
00:26:04,503 --> 00:26:06,133
But you can do that now.

340
00:26:06,133 --> 00:26:09,243
It's too late in this life.

341
00:26:09,243 --> 00:26:11,213
Hey, do you know how many smart people are in this world?

342
00:26:11,213 --> 00:26:14,683
I wouldn't be the first to think of, register, and develop something new.

343
00:26:14,683 --> 00:26:19,903
I tell you, sometimes, when a new idea comes to me, it will suddenly appear in real life!

344
00:26:19,903 --> 00:26:21,923
Gosh, seriously.

345
00:26:22,733 --> 00:26:28,323
I guess the only way for me to make money is through blood, sweat, and tears.

346
00:26:28,323 --> 00:26:30,543
It's because you're only thinking about them.

347
00:26:30,543 --> 00:26:33,213
You should try starting something first.

348
00:26:33,213 --> 00:26:37,353
Forget it! I plan to just live like this,

349
00:26:37,353 --> 00:26:40,923
then one day keel over and die without making a sound.

350
00:26:42,433 --> 00:26:46,113
That's bad luck! Hurry and take it back!

