00:26:48,583 --> 00:26:50,363
- Good morning! 
 - Yes!

352
00:26:50,363 --> 00:26:52,943
Good morning.

353
00:27:14,670 --> 00:27:18,000
- Get the numbers, and check up to the decimal points. 
 - Okay.

354
00:27:23,923 --> 00:27:28,703
Excuse me, may I please take a look at the financial statements?

355
00:27:28,703 --> 00:27:32,043
Sure, we already looked them over a few times.

356
00:27:32,043 --> 00:27:34,003
Thank you.

