00:29:29,683 --> 00:29:31,613
When Jang Ho Woo helps me, how should I put it?

388
00:29:31,613 --> 00:29:33,913
It feels more like we're being watched; it's not good.

389
00:29:33,913 --> 00:29:36,153
Right?

