00:29:49,073 --> 00:29:53,233
 I searched for the movie "Game Changer" that People's Ent. produced. 

396
00:29:53,233 --> 00:29:56,563
It's true that they had movie premieres last year and the year before.

397
00:29:56,563 --> 00:29:59,423
However, both movies had premieres, but neither was released.

398
00:29:59,423 --> 00:30:01,773
It's also odd no articles exist about the premieres.

