404
00:30:20,343 --> 00:30:23,203
Isn't it strange that celebrities are linked to the movie's inventory of assets—

405
00:30:23,203 --> 00:30:25,243
Mr. Jang Ho Woo!

406
00:30:30,083 --> 00:30:33,143
L-Let's go outside and talk for a minute.

