00:31:13,163 --> 00:31:15,423
Are you using your brain at all?

414
00:31:15,423 --> 00:31:18,733
Are you doing this knowing who Shim Hyung Woo is?

415
00:31:18,733 --> 00:31:21,983
- I know. 
 - You know?

416
00:31:21,983 --> 00:31:25,223
So you cut me down without discerning between friend or foe?

417
00:31:25,223 --> 00:31:27,573
